---
/** Static grid describing event formats (meetup, build session, cafe, hackathon). */
import SectionHeading from "@/components/SectionHeading.astro";
---

<div class="mb-24">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[#999999] uppercase tracking-widest">
      <span class="lang-en">What We Do</span>
      <span class="lang-ar">ماذا نقدم</span>
    </span>
    <SectionHeading id="event-types" class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white mt-3">
      <span class="lang-en">Our Events</span>
      <span class="lang-ar">فعالياتنا</span>
    </SectionHeading>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
    <!-- Cursor Meetup -->
    <div class="bg-[#171717] border border-[#252525] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
      <img src="/images/event-types/hackathon-riyadh.jpg" alt="Cursor meetups and community in Riyadh" class="w-full h-40 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#58a6ff] border border-[#58a6ff]/25 bg-[#58a6ff]/10 rounded px-2 py-1">
            <span class="lang-en">~2 hours</span>
            <span class="lang-ar">~ساعتين</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Cursor Meetup</span>
          <span class="lang-ar">لقاء كيرسر</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#999999] leading-relaxed">
          <span class="lang-en"
            >Knowledge-sharing meetups and workshops — talks, demos, and hands-on sessions covering Cursor workflows, MCP servers, prompt engineering, and AI-native development.</span
          >
          <span class="lang-ar"
            >لقاءات لنشر المعرفة — عروض تقديمية وجلسات عملية تغطي سير عمل كيرسر وخوادم MCP وهندسة البرومبت والتطوير بالذكاء الاصطناعي.</span
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Cursor Building Session -->
    <div class="bg-[#171717] border border-[#252525] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
      <img src="/images/event-types/building-session-riyadh.jpeg" alt="Cursor Building Session in Riyadh" class="w-full h-40 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-green-400 border border-green-400/25 bg-green-400/10 rounded px-2 py-1">
            <span class="lang-en">4–6 hours</span>
            <span class="lang-ar">٤-٦ ساعات</span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-amber-400 border border-amber-400/25 bg-amber-400/10 rounded px-2 py-1">
            <span class="lang-en">Free Credits</span>
            <span class="lang-ar">كريدتس مجانية</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Cursor Building Session</span>
          <span class="lang-ar">جلسة بناء كيرسر</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#999999] leading-relaxed">
          <span class="lang-en"
            >Hands-on building sessions where attendees ship real products using AI tools. Cursor provides free credits for all participants.</span
          >
          <span class="lang-ar"
            >جلسات بناء عملية يبني فيها الحضور منتجات حقيقية باستخدام أدوات الذكاء الاصطناعي. كيرسر يوفر كريدتس مجانية لجميع الحضور.</span
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Cafe Cursor -->
    <div class="bg-[#171717] border border-[#252525] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
      <img
        src="/images/event-types/cafe-cursor-sf.png"
        alt="Cafe Cursor, San Francisco"
        class="w-full h-40 object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-purple-400 border border-purple-400/25 bg-purple-400/10 rounded px-2 py-1">
            <span class="lang-en">6–12 hours</span>
            <span class="lang-ar">٦-١٢ ساعة</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Cafe Cursor</span>
          <span class="lang-ar">مقهى كيرسر</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#999999] leading-relaxed">
          <span class="lang-en"
            >Casual co-working at a local cafe — the same format Cursor runs globally (for example New York and San Francisco). We gather to work, network, and connect in a relaxed setting.</span
          >
          <span class="lang-ar"
            >عمل مشترك في مقهى محلي — نفس الأسلوب الذي تنظمه كيرسر عالمياً (مثل نيويورك وسان فرانسيسكو). نجتمع للعمل والتعارف والتواصل بأجواء مريحة.</span
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hackathon -->
    <div class="bg-[#171717] border border-[#252525] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
      <img src="/placeholders/event-card.svg" alt="" class="w-full h-40 object-cover bg-[#0d1117]" loading="lazy" />
      <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-red-400/80 border border-red-400/20 bg-red-400/5 rounded px-2 py-1">
            <span class="lang-en">~12 hours</span>
            <span class="lang-ar">~١٢ ساعة</span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-amber-400 border border-amber-400/25 bg-amber-400/10 rounded px-2 py-1">
            <span class="lang-en">Free Credits</span>
            <span class="lang-ar">كريدتس مجانية</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Cursor Hackathon</span>
          <span class="lang-ar">هاكاثون كيرسر</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#999999] leading-relaxed">
          <span class="lang-en"
            >Large-scale hackathons in partnership with local organizations — often a full ~12-hour day, with Cursor free credits for participants — building, competing, and shipping together.</span
          >
          <span class="lang-ar"
            >هاكاثونات كبيرة بشراكة مع جهات محلية — غالباً يوم كامل حوالي ١٢ ساعة، مع كريدتس مجانية من كيرسر للمشاركين — نبني ونتنافس وننجز معاً.</span
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
